text: Sky High Corral is a 1926 American silent western film directed by Clifford Smith and starring Art Acord, Marguerite Clayton and Duke R. Lee.Munden p.730 ==Cast== * Art Acord as Jack McCabe * Marguerite Clayton as Shasta Hayden * Duke R. Lee as Whitey Durk * Jack Mower as Burns * Thomas G. Lingham as Bill Hayden * Blackie Thompson as Gregg * Missouri Royer as Slim * Floyd Shackelford as Sam ==References== ==Bibliography== * Munden, Kenneth White. The American Film Institute Catalog of Motion Pictures Produced in the United States, Part 1.
